      "source": "#### JEP 500 â€” Prepare to Make Final Mean Final\n\nDemonstrate behavior around reflective mutation of `final` fields and related runtime flags in JDK 26.\n\nReferences:\n- JEP 500: https://openjdk.org/jeps/500\n- JFR event `jdk.FinalFieldMutation` (diagnostics)\n",
